texts.label: paragraph
texts.orig: There was a bug in versions of Plesk prior to 8.3 where the AWStats statistics for the previous months were unavailable. It was a bug within Plesk's AWStat's implementation, and it was fixed in Plesk 8.3.
texts.text: There was a bug in versions of Plesk prior to 8.3 where the AWStats statistics for the previous months were unavailable. It was a bug within Plesk's AWStat's implementation, and it was fixed in Plesk 8.3.

texts.label: paragraph
texts.orig: However, the fix only corrected the issue moving forward after the upgrade. There was no automated way to rebuild the previous months' statistics,  even though the AWStats data was right there on the disk !
texts.text: However, the fix only corrected the issue moving forward after the upgrade. There was no automated way to rebuild the previous months' statistics,  even though the AWStats data was right there on the disk !
